{"meta":{"instanceId":"bc8ca75c203589705ae2e446cad7181d6f2a7cc1766f958ef9f34810e53b8cb2","templateCredsSetupCompleted":true},"nodes":[{"id":"2beef53a-ddec-402a-9970-1f8934b48166","name":"Overview","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-1056,-336],"parameters":{"color":4,"width":524,"height":1236,"content":"## Webinar Recording to Salesforce Lead Follow-Up Email Generator — WayinVideo Summarization + GPT-4o-mini + Salesforce + Gmail + Sheets\n\nFor marketing teams, sales teams, and agencies who run webinars and want to automatically send a personalized follow-up email to every registered Salesforce lead within minutes of the webinar ending — referencing specific content covered — instead of sending a generic broadcast. Submit the webinar recording URL via the form. WayinVideo Summarization API generates a structured summary with numbered highlights and tags. GPT-4o-mini writes a personalized email per lead — addressing them by first name, referencing their role and company, and citing 2–3 specific highlights from the webinar. Gmail sends each email. Salesforce logs a completed Task activity on each lead record. Google Sheets logs every send with the Salesforce Task ID.\n\n## How it works\n- **1. Form — Webinar URL + Details** collects the recording URL, webinar title, host name, company name, webinar date, and CTA link\n- **2. WayinVideo — Submit Summarization** submits the URL to the Summarization API\n- **3. Wait — 90 Seconds** gives the API initial processing time\n- **4. WayinVideo — Get Summary Results** polls the summaries results endpoint\n- **5. IF — Summary Complete?** checks for SUCCEEDED — if not, retries via 30-second wait\n- **7. Code — Extract Summary Data** extracts summary, numbered highlights, and all form fields into a clean object\n- **8. Salesforce — Query Registered Leads** runs SOQL to fetch all leads where Webinar_Name__c matches the webinar title, limit 500\n- **9. AI Agent — Write Personalized Email** uses GPT-4o-mini to write a 150–200 word personalized email per lead with subject line, personalized intro, and full body\n- **11. Code — Parse Email Output** extracts 3 labeled sections via regex and assembles all lead and webinar fields\n- **12. Gmail — Send Follow-Up Email** sends the personalized email to each lead's email address\n- **13. Salesforce — Log Email as Activity** creates a completed Task on each lead record with WhoId association\n- **14. Google Sheets — Log Follow-Up** logs all 10 fields including Salesforce Task ID\n\n## Set up steps\n1. In **2** and **4** — replace `YOUR_WAYINVIDEO_API_KEY`\n2. In **10. OpenAI — GPT-4o-mini Model** — connect your OpenAI credential\n3. In **8** and **13** — connect your Salesforce OAuth2 credential\n4. In **12** — connect your Gmail OAuth2 credential\n5. In **14** — connect your Google Sheets OAuth2 credential and replace `YOUR_GOOGLE_SHEET_ID`\n6. In your Salesforce org — ensure the Lead object has a custom field `Webinar_Name__c` populated at registration. If your field name is different, edit the SOQL query in node 8\n7. Create a Google Sheet tab named Follow-up Log with columns: Webinar Title, Lead Email, Lead Name, Lead Company, Email Subject, Personalized Intro, Salesforce Lead ID, Salesforce Task ID, Sent Status, Sent On"},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"4e580dee-4281-41c6-bf4f-a626e9d7dd32","name":"Section — Form Input","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-528,-80],"parameters":{"color":5,"width":372,"height":356,"content":"## Form Input\nMarketing team submits webinar recording URL, webinar title, host name, company name, webinar date, and CTA link. All six fields feed into summary extraction and the AI personalization prompt."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"c79bc7c4-25b1-4022-a4ed-434eaac05608","name":"Section — WayinVideo Summarization Submit and Poll","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-144,-80],"parameters":{"color":6,"width":724,"height":356,"content":"## WayinVideo Summarization Submit and Poll\nSubmits the webinar URL to the Summarization API. Waits 90 seconds for initial processing. Polls the results endpoint until status equals SUCCEEDED."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"4f1ee529-8e5d-4ec9-8fb5-fc94e80a0aae","name":"Section — Summary Status Check and Retry Loop","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[608,-240],"parameters":{"color":6,"width":308,"height":880,"content":"## Summary Status Check and Retry Loop\nIF checks for SUCCEEDED status. TRUE proceeds to summary extraction. FALSE waits 30 seconds and polls again. Loop continues until summary is ready."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"fa7c55ac-77fc-4890-8044-9cdb78413fcc","name":"Section — Summary Extraction and Salesforce Lead Query","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[944,-112],"parameters":{"color":6,"width":420,"height":484,"content":"## Summary Extraction and Salesforce Lead Query\nCode node formats summary text, numbered highlights, and all form fields into one clean object. Salesforce SOQL query fetches up to 500 unconverted leads where Webinar_Name__c matches the title."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"8cae0076-4115-4ef6-81c6-0d40dbc166b2","name":"Section — Per-Lead AI Email Writing","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[1424,-192],"parameters":{"color":6,"width":308,"height":764,"content":"## Per-Lead AI Email Writing\nGPT-4o-mini writes a personalized 150–200 word follow-up email per lead — addressing them by first name, referencing their role and company, and citing 2–3 specific webinar highlights."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"638094aa-b097-443b-a400-cb4215fbddfc","name":"Section — Email Parse, Gmail Send, Salesforce Task Log, and Sheet Log","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[1744,-64],"parameters":{"color":4,"width":964,"height":436,"content":"## Email Parse, Gmail Send, Salesforce Task Log, and Sheet Log\nRegex extracts 3 sections. Gmail sends the personalized email. Salesforce creates a completed Task activity on the lead record with WhoId. Google Sheets logs all fields including the Salesforce Task ID."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"e2d0e819-1d71-4740-ac51-e67222ed82af","name":"1. Form — Webinar URL + Details","type":"n8n-nodes-base.formTrigger","position":[-384,80],"webhookId":"d98777ef-9500-4389-8aad-1b9dc23b6b97","parameters":{"options":{},"formTitle":"Webinar Follow-Up Email Generator","formFields":{"values":[{"fieldLabel":"Webinar Recording URL","placeholder":"https://zoom.us/rec/xxxxxxx or YouTube/Vimeo link","requiredField":true},{"fieldLabel":"Webinar Title","placeholder":"e.g. Advanced SEO Strategies for 2025","requiredField":true},{"fieldLabel":"Host / Speaker Name","placeholder":"e.g. John Smith","requiredField":true},{"fieldLabel":"Company / Brand Name","placeholder":"e.g. Incrementors, Acme Corp","requiredField":true},{"fieldLabel":"Webinar Date","placeholder":"e.g. 2025-04-29","requiredField":true},{"fieldLabel":"CTA Link","placeholder":"e.g. https://yoursite.com/book-a-call or https://yoursite.com/course","requiredField":true}]},"formDescription":"Paste your webinar recording URL. AI will summarize the session and automatically send a personalized follow-up email to every registered lead in Salesforce."},"typeVersion":2.2},{"id":"821b1ebf-c226-48fa-9d38-ccb950fd4581","name":"2. WayinVideo — Submit Summarization","type":"n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest","position":[-80,80],"parameters":{"url":"https://wayinvideo-api.wayin.ai/api/v2/summaries","method":"POST","options":{},"jsonBody":"={\n  \"video_url\": \"{{ $json['Webinar Recording URL'] }}\",\n  \"target_lang\": \"en\"\n}","sendBody":true,"sendHeaders":true,"specifyBody":"json","headerParameters":{"parameters":[{"name":"Authorization","value":"Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE"},{"name":"x-wayinvideo-api-version","value":"v2"},{"name":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}]}},"typeVersion":4.2},{"id":"838cbc20-ed3d-4b8c-9426-16286acbbda5","name":"3. Wait — 90 Seconds","type":"n8n-nodes-base.wait","position":[176,80],"webhookId":"wait-salesforce-followup-90s","parameters":{"amount":90},"typeVersion":1.1},{"id":"4fc26272-e812-4c67-aab7-756a711d1831","name":"4. WayinVideo — Get Summary Results","type":"n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest","position":[432,80],"parameters":{"url":"=https://wayinvideo-api.wayin.ai/api/v2/summaries/results/{{ $('2. WayinVideo — Submit Summarization').item.json.data.id }}","options":{},"sendHeaders":true,"headerParameters":{"parameters":[{"name":"Authorization","value":"Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE"},{"name":"x-wayinvideo-api-version","value":"v2"},{"name":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}]}},"typeVersion":4.2},{"id":"3eb4bebb-e378-4e4d-b75a-54582e81c9df","name":"5. IF — Summary Complete?","type":"n8n-nodes-base.if","position":[688,80],"parameters":{"options":{},"conditions":{"options":{"version":3,"leftValue":"","caseSensitive":true,"typeValidation":"loose"},"combinator":"and","conditions":[{"id":"status-check","operator":{"type":"string","operation":"equals"},"leftValue":"={{ $json.data.status }}","rightValue":"SUCCEEDED"}]}},"typeVersion":2.3},{"id":"d42bd2ba-dd1f-4563-bed6-7c942ee76a15","name":"6. Wait — 30 Seconds Retry","type":"n8n-nodes-base.wait","position":[704,336],"webhookId":"wait-salesforce-retry-30s","parameters":{"amount":30},"typeVersion":1.1},{"id":"95e82089-f79b-475a-9136-3c6482748327","name":"7. Code — Extract Summary Data","type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","position":[992,80],"parameters":{"jsCode":"// Extract summary data from WayinVideo\nconst summaryData = $('4. WayinVideo — Get Summary Results').item.json.data;\n\nconst summary = summaryData.summary || '';\nconst highlights = Array.isArray(summaryData.highlights)\n  ? summaryData.highlights.map((h, i) => `${i + 1}. ${h.desc}`).join('\\n')\n  : '';\nconst tags = Array.isArray(summaryData.tags)\n  ? summaryData.tags.join(', ')\n  : '';\n\n// Get form data\nconst webinarTitle = $('1. Form — Webinar URL + Details').item.json['Webinar Title'];\nconst hostName = $('1. Form — Webinar URL + Details').item.json['Host / Speaker Name'];\nconst companyName = $('1. Form — Webinar URL + Details').item.json['Company / Brand Name'];\nconst webinarDate = $('1. Form — Webinar URL + Details').item.json['Webinar Date'];\nconst ctaLink = $('1. Form — Webinar URL + Details').item.json['CTA Link'];\nconst recordingUrl = $('1. Form — Webinar URL + Details').item.json['Webinar Recording URL'];\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    summary,\n    highlights,\n    tags,\n    webinarTitle,\n    hostName,\n    companyName,\n    webinarDate,\n    ctaLink,\n    recordingUrl\n  }\n}];"},"typeVersion":2},{"id":"dbca6458-8621-455b-9ff7-0a593e89fb70","name":"8. Salesforce — Query Registered Leads","type":"n8n-nodes-base.salesforce","position":[1232,80],"parameters":{"operation":"query"},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"7adf24b6-39b5-49d4-b62c-4a249d592f60","name":"9. AI Agent — Write Personalized Email","type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent","position":[1472,80],"parameters":{"text":"=Write a personalized follow-up email for this lead who attended our webinar.\n\nLead Details:\n- First Name: {{ $json.FirstName }}\n- Last Name: {{ $json.LastName }}\n- Email: {{ $json.Email }}\n- Company: {{ $json.Company }}\n- Job Title: {{ $json.Title || 'N/A' }}\n\nWebinar Details:\n- Webinar Title: {{ $('7. Code — Extract Summary Data').item.json.webinarTitle }}\n- Host: {{ $('7. Code — Extract Summary Data').item.json.hostName }}\n- Company: {{ $('7. Code — Extract Summary Data').item.json.companyName }}\n- Date: {{ $('7. Code — Extract Summary Data').item.json.webinarDate }}\n- CTA Link: {{ $('7. Code — Extract Summary Data').item.json.ctaLink }}\n- Recording URL: {{ $('7. Code — Extract Summary Data').item.json.recordingUrl }}\n\nWebinar Summary:\n{{ $('7. Code — Extract Summary Data').item.json.summary }}\n\nKey Highlights Covered:\n{{ $('7. Code — Extract Summary Data').item.json.highlights }}\n\n---\n\nWrite a personalized follow-up email following these rules:\n\n1. Address the lead by their first name\n2. Reference 2-3 specific things from the webinar highlights that are relevant to someone in their role or industry\n3. Keep it conversational and warm — not salesy\n4. Include a clear next step with the CTA link\n5. Include the recording URL so they can rewatch\n6. Total length: 150-200 words — short and easy to read\n7. End with the host's name as signature\n\nReturn in this exact format:\n\nSUBJECT_LINE:\n[Write subject line — 45-55 chars — reference the webinar topic]\n\nPERSONALIZED_INTRO:\n[Write 1-2 sentence personalized opening that references their role or company]\n\nEMAIL_BODY:\n[Write the full email body — 150-200 words — no subject line — starts with Hi [FirstName],]","options":{},"promptType":"define"},"typeVersion":3.1},{"id":"cde1f291-2400-4e4c-903f-202b1654b9f4","name":"10. OpenAI — GPT-4o-mini Model","type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.lmChatOpenAi","position":[1472,288],"parameters":{"model":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"gpt-4o-mini"},"options":{},"builtInTools":{}},"typeVersion":1.3},{"id":"c46582eb-8a20-46f8-acb6-b7fc5dd6a68c","name":"11. Code — Parse Email Output","type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","position":[1792,80],"parameters":{"jsCode":"// Parse AI email output\nconst output = $input.first().json.output || '';\n\n// Extract subject line\nconst subjectMatch = output.match(/SUBJECT_LINE:\\s*([\\s\\S]*?)(?=\\nPERSONALIZED_INTRO:|$)/);\nconst introMatch = output.match(/PERSONALIZED_INTRO:\\s*([\\s\\S]*?)(?=\\nEMAIL_BODY:|$)/);\nconst bodyMatch = output.match(/EMAIL_BODY:\\s*([\\s\\S]*)$/);\n\nconst subjectLine = subjectMatch ? subjectMatch[1].trim() : `Re: ${$('7. Code — Extract Summary Data').item.json.webinarTitle}`;\nconst personalizedIntro = introMatch ? introMatch[1].trim() : '';\nconst emailBody = bodyMatch ? bodyMatch[1].trim() : output;\n\n// Get lead data\nconst leadId = $('8. Salesforce — Query Registered Leads').item.json.Id;\nconst leadEmail = $('8. Salesforce — Query Registered Leads').item.json.Email;\nconst leadFirstName = $('8. Salesforce — Query Registered Leads').item.json.FirstName;\nconst leadLastName = $('8. Salesforce — Query Registered Leads').item.json.LastName;\nconst leadCompany = $('8. Salesforce — Query Registered Leads').item.json.Company;\n\n// Get webinar data\nconst webinarTitle = $('7. Code — Extract Summary Data').item.json.webinarTitle;\nconst companyName = $('7. Code — Extract Summary Data').item.json.companyName;\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    subjectLine,\n    personalizedIntro,\n    emailBody,\n    leadId,\n    leadEmail,\n    leadFirstName,\n    leadLastName,\n    leadCompany,\n    webinarTitle,\n    companyName\n  }\n}];"},"typeVersion":2},{"id":"ab398ef0-5332-41fb-b00e-d4a067d220ef","name":"12. Gmail — Send Follow-Up Email","type":"n8n-nodes-base.gmail","position":[2032,80],"webhookId":"bacf4f4f-d5e7-4b44-9726-d68ce1c7a508","parameters":{"sendTo":"={{ $json.leadEmail }}","message":"={{ $json.emailBody }}","options":{"senderName":"={{ $json.companyName }}"},"subject":"={{ $json.subjectLine }}"},"typeVersion":2.1},{"id":"6e604604-3836-4caa-b26c-be282ec1366d","name":"13. Salesforce — Log Email as Activity","type":"n8n-nodes-base.salesforce","position":[2272,80],"parameters":{"additionalFields":{"customFieldsUi":{"customFieldsValues":[{"value":"=Webinar Follow-Up Email Sent — {{ $('11. Code — Parse Email Output').item.json.webinarTitle }}","fieldId":"Subject"},{"value":"Completed","fieldId":"Status"},{"value":"Normal","fieldId":"Priority"},{"value":"={{ $now.toFormat('yyyy-MM-dd') }}","fieldId":"ActivityDate"},{"value":"=Automated follow-up email sent after webinar: {{ $('11. Code — Parse Email Output').item.json.webinarTitle }}\\n\\nEmail Subject: {{ $('11. Code — Parse Email Output').item.json.subjectLine }}\\n\\nSent to: {{ $('11. Code — Parse Email Output').item.json.leadEmail }}","fieldId":"Description"},{"value":"={{ $('11. Code — Parse Email Output').item.json.leadId }}","fieldId":"WhoId"}]}}},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"8d244d63-cbc1-4610-bd8c-b2d3665c2725","name":"14. Google Sheets — Log Follow-Up","type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","position":[2512,80],"parameters":{"columns":{"value":{"Sent On":"={{ $now.toFormat('dd MMMM yyyy HH:mm') }}","Lead Name":"={{ $('11. Code — Parse Email Output').item.json.leadFirstName }} {{ $('11. Code — Parse Email Output').item.json.leadLastName }}","Lead Email":"={{ $('11. Code — Parse Email Output').item.json.leadEmail }}","Sent Status":"Sent","Lead Company":"={{ $('11. Code — Parse Email Output').item.json.leadCompany }}","Email Subject":"={{ $('11. Code — Parse Email Output').item.json.subjectLine }}","Webinar Title":"={{ $('11. Code — Parse Email Output').item.json.webinarTitle }}","Personalized Intro":"={{ $('11. Code — Parse Email Output').item.json.personalizedIntro }}","Salesforce Lead ID":"={{ $('11. Code — Parse Email Output').item.json.leadId }}","Salesforce Task ID":"={{ $json.id }}"},"schema":[],"mappingMode":"defineBelow","matchingColumns":[]},"options":{},"operation":"append","sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Follow-up Log"},"documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"id","value":"YOUR_GOOGLE_SHEET_ID"}},"typeVersion":4.5}],"pinData":{},"connections":{"3. Wait — 90 Seconds":{"main":[[{"node":"4. WayinVideo — Get Summary Results","type":"main","index":0}]]},"5. IF — Summary Complete?":{"main":[[{"node":"7. Code — Extract Summary Data","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"6. Wait — 30 Seconds Retry","type":"main","index":0}]]},"6. Wait — 30 Seconds Retry":{"main":[[{"node":"4. WayinVideo — Get Summary Results","type":"main","index":0}]]},"11. Code — Parse Email Output":{"main":[[{"node":"12. Gmail — Send Follow-Up Email","type":"main","index":0}]]},"10. OpenAI — GPT-4o-mini Model":{"ai_languageModel":[[{"node":"9. AI Agent — Write Personalized Email","type":"ai_languageModel","index":0}]]},"7. Code — Extract Summary Data":{"main":[[{"node":"8. Salesforce — Query Registered Leads","type":"main","index":0}]]},"1. Form — Webinar URL + Details":{"main":[[{"node":"2. WayinVideo — Submit Summarization","type":"main","index":0}]]},"12. Gmail — Send Follow-Up Email":{"main":[[{"node":"13. Salesforce — Log Email as Activity","type":"main","index":0}]]},"4. WayinVideo — Get Summary Results":{"main":[[{"node":"5. IF — Summary Complete?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"2. WayinVideo — Submit Summarization":{"main":[[{"node":"3. Wait — 90 Seconds","type":"main","index":0}]]},"13. Salesforce — Log Email as Activity":{"main":[[{"node":"14. Google Sheets — Log Follow-Up","type":"main","index":0}]]},"8. Salesforce — Query Registered Leads":{"main":[[{"node":"9. AI Agent — Write Personalized Email","type":"main","index":0}]]},"9. AI Agent — Write Personalized Email":{"main":[[{"node":"11. Code — Parse Email Output","type":"main","index":0}]]}}}